<section id="Viewing_the_SmartProxy_Log" remap="TID_15087">
	<title>Viewing the SmartProxy Log</title>
	<para>
		Use the logs to troubleshoot communications and operational events of the SmartProxy. The server gets the log on demand.
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>To View the SmartProxy Log</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Configure</guimenu><guisubmenu>Smartproxies</guisubmenu></menuchoice>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click the SmartProxy with the log you want to view.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				From the <guilabel>SmartProxy</guilabel> accordion, click <guilabel>Properties</guilabel>, and then <guilabel>Log Viewer</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click 
				<inlinemediaobject>
					<imageobject>
						<imagedata fileref="images/2003.png" />
					</imageobject>
				</inlinemediaobject> (<guilabel>Retrieve the current SmartProxy log</guilabel>) to get the latest log from the SmartProxy.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Refresh your browser.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>